ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
PrecisReappointment of RICHARD DICERNI, C.M., of Ottawa, Ontario, as a part-time member of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police; and his designation as Chairperson of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, effective December 2, 2020.
